{"tid":1005373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左澳門，差唔多所有華人地區都有歌手踏上過華語金曲獎的舞台","createTime":"2019-02-02T07:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T06:50:31.000Z","uid":100680,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"bacba8c6dc655a069ccac6cea5c61c502a441a19","tid":1005373,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:24:09.000Z","msg":"金曲獎被譽為華語音樂的殿堂<br />\n本身就係要你有高水準唱功＋作品先會被金曲獎邀請<br />\n要入圍都唔係好容易的事，更遑論拿獎<br />\n但原來我地香港人真係唔差，除左台灣，入圍最多的華人地區真係香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港 --- 張學友，陳奕迅，何韻詩，林憶蓮，葉倩文，GEM，劉德華，方大同，周華健，莫文蔚<br />\n新加坡　&mdash;　林俊傑，孫燕姿，陳綺貞，蔡健雅<br />\n中國　&mdash;　那英，王菲<br />\n馬來西亞　&mdash;　梁靜茹，曹格，戴佩妮<br />\n台灣　&mdash;　一堆，不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n澳門　&mdash;　無"},{"pid":"b47b21cf93a127dbd5fb0b5fce01ec00adccd190","tid":1005373,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":35,"score":-30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"獎項打飛機用<br />\n講唱功張靚穎 韓紅點會低過上面班人"},{"pid":"050f1ddaa2dd015dd8aa6a7dbda3c12a7beabaac","tid":1005373,"uid":100680,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b47b21cf93a127dbd5fb0b5fce01ec00adccd190","tid":1005373,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":35,"score":-30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"獎項打飛機用<br />\n講唱功張靚穎 韓紅點會低過上面班人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"要有高水準唱功＋作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n計唱功張惠妹都好勁，但佢早期唱黎唱去都係慘情Ｋ歌結果俾金曲獎掃出門，係到後期轉型唱多種唔同風格的歌先拿到女歌手獎"},{"pid":"3ac890cec7748773cc1432530a13c110b551da3e","tid":1005373,"uid":127569,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"澳門人=垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285c249ab12ff825122da2b491ceda04c7f5490e","tid":1005373,"uid":188396,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b47b21cf93a